14:28:04.280 [INFO] related_entity: Miles Novak
14:28:04.280 [INFO] lines:
14:28:04.280 [INFO]   - item: Cloud instance
14:28:04.280 [INFO]     quantity: 1
14:28:04.280 [INFO]     unit_eur: 200
14:28:04.280 [INFO]     line_eur: 200
14:28:04.280 [INFO]   - item: Backup storage
